text: Nuhiu is an Albanian surname. Notable people with this name include: * Agim Nuhiu (born 1977), Macedonian politician * Ardian Nuhiu (born 1978), Macedonian footballer * Atdhe Nuhiu (born 1989), Kosovo footballer * Donika Nuhiu (born 1999), Albanian singer Category:Albanian-language surnames
title: Nuhiu
